{"tid":2493580,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[恐懼之間]多人推理遊戲","createTime":"2021-04-18T04:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T05:31:39.000Z","uid":140852,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a3a53a79ce70a0f13b0e36801838b0d8487ba692","tid":2493580,"uid":140852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:26:31.000Z","msg":"玩法同Among us一樣<br />\n但呢個遊戲係第一身視角<br />\n同埋有職業系統<br />\n所以討論過程比較多野盤<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVAvLxBvih7CLUo6w8Whg5YPqS8xj2mfn8DywFdPx1i79?filename=TaUuw8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTaUuw8c.jpg&h=4cc97b5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n好人時內做任務可以贏得遊戲<br />\n鬼要限時內殺好人贏得遊戲<br />\n<br />\n祭壇 : 拍台的意思 - 120秒<br />\n<br />\n好人陣營（不做任務會流血而死）<br />\n旅行者 : 沒有技能<br />\n牧師 : 驗一個人好定壞 - 禁用(太強了)<br />\n法醫 : 驗出有沒有死屍，有死屍會見到紅色圈 - 90秒冷卻<br />\n白靈 : 殺一個人 - 只限一次<br />\n白痴 : 被投票不會出局， 但之後不能再投票<br />\n<br />\n惡靈陣營 : <br />\n鬼陣營 :（不做任務不會死）<br />\n關燈鬼 : 能關燈 10 秒 - 90秒冷卻<br />\n透視鬼 : 看到全場人的位置 10 秒 - 50秒冷卻<br />\n隱魔 : 被牧師查是好人，一開始沒有刀，雙鬼死後才有刀<br />\n背叛者 : 沒有技能，投票無效，發言階段幫鬼說謊 (鬼和背叛需要找對方出來)<br />\n<br />\n正常係玩 10人局/12人局<br />\n10人屠邊<br />\n好人 : 法醫 白靈<br />\n惡靈 : 關燈 透視 背叛<br />\n<br />\n12人屠邊<br />\n好人 : 法醫 白靈 白痴<br />\n惡靈 : 關燈 透視 隱鬼 背叛<br />\n<br />\n呢個遊戲內置係輪流發言<br />\n變相係正規狼人殺玩法<br />\n我地認為呢種玩法太悶<br />\n所以通常都係私下約局用Discord玩<br />\n咁就可以同時發言<br />\n而且比人屈既時候可以反駁<br />\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/G38cb9DsDj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FG38cb9DsDj&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RLhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=3e2bf360\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/G38cb9DsDj</a>"},{"pid":"2b794d25c304e30174de884ddddc4934eaabbb72","tid":2493580,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:39:07.000Z","msg":"App?"},{"pid":"391648e4f557361cfd5cc34d97198f8a7871e6d1","tid":2493580,"uid":140852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b794d25c304e30174de884ddddc4934eaabbb72","tid":2493580,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:39:07.000Z","msg":"App?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:41:17.000Z","msg":"Sorry<br />\n原來無貼遊戲Link<br />\n<br />\n恐懼之間 Fear surrounds<br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/1526490/_Fear_surrounds/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F1526490%2F_Fear_surrounds%2F&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RLhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=6b50f4a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/1526490/_Fear_surrounds/</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然遊戲風格有點恐怖風<br />\n但遊戲核心都係邏輯推理搵兇手<br />\n所以遊戲設定可以Set將恐怖畫面(關)"},{"pid":"c2f07ff02d59e208f8bd937a34fb5d61664a4b96","tid":2493580,"uid":140852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T05:31:39.000Z","msg":"推"}]}